It's my personal ~/.vim/ repository
Just use for macbook
Install nerdfont for icons

安装vim8 并且支持python3
参考我的另外一个项目zsh配置， 安装oh-my-zsh和powerline-status 以及zsh插件

#搜索功能ag, ack
brew install the_silver_searcher Ack ripgrep
#tags
brew install ctags
#font字体图标
brew tap homebrew/cask-fonts
brew install --cask font-hack-nerd-font


#for coc.vim autocompeletion
brew install node
brew install npm && npm install --global prettier
npm i eslint eslint-plugin-vue -D
npm install --global htmlhint
npm install yarn
npm install -g neovim

pip3 install pylint
pip3 install flake8
pip3 install pyflakes
pip3 install black
pip3 install isort
pip3 install autopep8
pip3 install pynvim==0.4.3
pip3 install --user powerline-status
